363.last_action: Education Deferred to the 41st legislative day, Passed, YEAS 5, NAYS 2. S.J. 160
363.title: Declare void the transgender procedure adopted by the South Dakota High School Activities Association and to establish a determinant in identifying a student's sexual identity for the purpose of participation in high school athletics.
